try to wear some clothes,
okay, Beercules?

19:04.747 --> 19:06.046
Wow! That's a big snake.

19:06.048 --> 19:07.214
Oh, there's
a snake in the swamp?

19:07.216 --> 19:08.665
No, I'm talking about
your penis.

19:08.667 --> 19:09.983
See you tomorrow.

19:11.536 --> 19:12.419
I got the job.

19:12.421 --> 19:13.870
Yay!

19:13.872 --> 19:16.306
And I think that my boss
already sexually harassed me.

19:16.308 --> 19:18.892
But he saw the video
and he doesn't care!

19:18.894 --> 19:21.812
See that? Maybe Beercules
isn't so bad after all.

19:21.814 --> 19:22.763
Yeah.

19:24.150 --> 19:25.215
Hello?

19:25.217 --> 19:27.734
Hey, Marshall,
my name is Pete Durkenson.

19:27.736 --> 19:29.153
We went to Wesleyan together.

19:29.155 --> 19:30.404
Yeah, no, I know.

19:30.406 --> 19:32.606
Pete, we... we just
hung out yesterday.

19:32.608 --> 19:34.825
All right, now Lily's message
makes a little more sense.

19:34.827 --> 19:37.361
Listen, don't worry, bro,
I'm gonna take down the video.

19:37.363 --> 19:38.579
You know what?

19:38.581 --> 19:40.063
Leave it up.

19:40.065 --> 19:41.832
Whatever you say, Beercules.

19:44.786 --> 19:46.703
Scalpel.

19:46.705 --> 19:48.922
You know what?
This is good.

19:48.924 --> 19:51.341
I want our kid to see
every side of who I am.

19:51.343 --> 19:52.593
Yeah.

19:52.595 --> 19:54.077
Even the side that runs through

19:54.079 --> 19:56.196
the East Village hangin' brain.

19:57.765 --> 19:59.133
I'm gonna call Pete back.

19:59.135 --> 20:00.551
That's a good idea.

20:00.553 --> 20:03.753
<i>That evening, I took</i>
<i>Robin to the Architects' Ball.</i>

20:03.755 --> 20:05.439
Thanks again for
taking me to this.

20:05.441 --> 20:06.473
Mm. My pleasure.

20:06.475 --> 20:07.774
And, you know, you might
find it interesting.

20:07.776 --> 20:09.893
Some of these guys represent the
living history of New York--

20:09.895 --> 20:11.261
Yeah, yeah.
Where's Lenny Kravitz?

20:11.263 --> 20:12.929
Right there.

20:12.931 --> 20:16.783
Leonard Kravitz,
world-renowned architect.

20:16.785 --> 20:19.036
Guy's a rock star.

20:19.038 --> 20:20.654
He's gonna be
giving his famous

20:20.656 --> 20:22.039
90-minute lecture
on crossbeams.

20:22.041 --> 20:23.540
Well, great.

20:23.542 --> 20:25.826
I'm gonna go find one
and hang myself from it.

20:25.828 --> 20:27.244
Okay.

20:27.246 --> 20:30.130
<i>Kids, you can't talk</i>
<i>yourself into falling in love.</i>

20:30.132 --> 20:32.949
<i>It doesn't take days</i>
<i>of deliberation.</i>

20:32.951 --> 20:36.503
<i>When it's real,</i>
<i>you know pretty quickly,</i>

20:36.505 --> 20:39.789
<i>and with absolute certainty.</i>

20:41.059 --> 20:43.627
<i>I had forgotten that.</i>

